title: Private 1Bed/1Bath available in 5 bedroom house
posting_body: We have a private room available at our house starting August 29th.
It’s a 2 story house with lots of street parking and a garage.
We are located near Taraval street that has many bars, restaurants, markets and Muni L/ bus transportation.
Short walk to the beach and easy access to freeways.
This is a private room with your own bathroom.
We have a laundry room in the garage and lots of storage space.
First and last months rent is required.
Sorry, no pets allowed due to landlords policy.
Message me for more details and happy house hunting!
